  <header>
    <h1>iOS Development</h1>
    <p>Master iOS app development with Swift, SwiftUI, and modern Apple frameworks.</p>
  </header>
  
  <section id="fundamentals">
    <h2 class="section-title">Swift Fundamentals</h2>
    <div class="tech-grid">
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Swift Programming</h3>
        <p>Learn Swift programming language fundamentals, including syntax, optionals, protocols, and modern features.</p>
        <a href="https://docs.swift.org/swift-book/documentation/the-swift-programming-language/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>SwiftUI</h3>
        <p>Master Apple's modern declarative framework for building user interfaces across all Apple platforms.</p>
        <a href="https://developer.apple.com/xcode/swiftui/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>UIKit</h3>
        <p>Understand the traditional iOS UI framework for building complex user interfaces programmatically.</p>
        <a href="https://developer.apple.com/documentation/uikit" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section id="frameworks">
    <h2 class="section-title">Essential iOS Frameworks</h2>
    <div class="tech-grid">
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Core Data</h3>
        <p>Learn data persistence and management with Apple's object graph and persistence framework.</p>
        <a href="https://developer.apple.com/documentation/coredata" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Core Animation</h3>
        <p>Create fluid animations and visual effects in your iOS applications.</p>
        <a href="https://developer.apple.com/documentation/quartzcore" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Core ML</h3>
        <p>Integrate machine learning models into your iOS apps for intelligent features.</p>
        <a href="https://developer.apple.com/documentation/coreml" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="design">
    <h2 class="section-title">UI Design for iOS</h2>
    <div class="tech-grid">
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Human Interface Guidelines</h3>
        <p>Learn Apple's design principles for creating intuitive and user-friendly iOS apps.</p>
        <a href="https://developer.apple.com/design/human-interface-guidelines/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>SwiftUI Design</h3>
        <p>Master SwiftUI's declarative syntax to create beautiful and responsive user interfaces.</p>
        <a href="https://developer.apple.com/xcode/swiftui/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>UIKit Design</h3>
        <p>Understand UIKit's components and how to build custom views for complex UI requirements.</p>
        <a href="https://developer.apple.com/documentation/uikit" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Prototyping with Figma</h3>
        <p>Use Figma to create interactive prototypes and collaborate on app designs with your team.</p>
        <a href="https://www.figma.com/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Accessibility</h3>
        <p>Ensure your app is accessible to all users by following Apple's accessibility guidelines.</p>
        <a href="https://developer.apple.com/accessibility/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="tech-card">
        <h3>Design Systems</h3>
        <p>Learn how to create reusable design systems for consistency across your app's UI.</p>
        <a href="https://material.io/design" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section id="roadmap">
    <h2 class="section-title">iOS Development Roadmap</h2>
    <div class="roadmap">
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>1. Swift Basics</h3>
        <p>Master Swift syntax, data types, control flow, and object-oriented programming concepts.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>2. iOS Fundamentals</h3>
        <p>Learn app lifecycle, view controllers, and basic UI components.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>3. UI Development</h3>
        <p>Master SwiftUI and understand UIKit for building modern interfaces.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>4. Data & Networking</h3>
        <p>Learn Core Data, networking with URLSession, and JSON parsing.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>5. Advanced Topics</h3>
        <p>Explore concurrency, memory management, and app architecture patterns.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="roadmap-step">
        <h3>6. App Store & Distribution</h3>
        <p>Understand certificates, provisioning profiles, and App Store submission process.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
